{"about_the_game":"In this game, you play as a lone survivor who previously opposed technology on an island destroyed by its technological advancements. As the sole survivor, you struggle to stay alive in a wilderness inhabited by dangerous enemies. Explore, gather, and manage your resources to survive. Your survival rests on your ability to acclimate to your environment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INTERACTIVE OPEN WORLD</h2>In this vast open world game, the player can access almost every part of the world. Discover hidden paths and multiple levels as you explore different places throughout the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DAY AND NIGHT CYCLE</h2>With features like a day and night cycle, the complexity of the game changes completely, wait until darkness to venture out and the hunter will become the hunted.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DYNAMIC WEATHER &amp; SEASONS</h2>Dynamic weather brings a more realistic aspect to the game. Experience varying difficulties of survival with the changing of the seasons, from sunburn and increased exhaustion during summer to experiencing frostbite in the winter.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CREATIVE BUILDING</h2>You can't have a survival game without building and we have added just that and more. Experience building on a whole new level with multiple combinations of materials and prefabs you can make your base how you want it.</ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1691253144","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918630/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1691253144","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918630/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1691253144","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918630/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1691253144","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"In this game, you play as a lone survivor who previously opposed technology on an island destroyed by its technological advancements. As the sole survivor, you struggle to stay alive in a wilderness inhabited by dangerous enemies. Explore, gather, and manage your resources to survive. Your survival rests on your ability to acclimate to your environment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INTERACTIVE OPEN WORLD</h2>In this vast open world game, the player can access almost every part of the world. Discover hidden paths and multiple levels as you explore different places throughout the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DAY AND NIGHT CYCLE</h2>With features like a day and night cycle, the complexity of the game changes completely, wait until darkness to venture out and the hunter will become the hunted.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DYNAMIC WEATHER &amp; SEASONS</h2>Dynamic weather brings a more realistic aspect to the game. Experience varying difficulties of survival with the changing of the seasons, from sunburn and increased exhaustion during summer to experiencing frostbite in the winter.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CREATIVE BUILDING</h2>You can't have a survival game without building and we have added just that and more. Experience building on a whole new level with multiple combinations of materials and prefabs you can make your base how you want it.</ul>","developers":["Madd Game Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918630/header.jpg?t=1691253144","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"name":"Acclimate","package_groups":